<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight">What Questions Should You Ask a Baltimore Wedding Photographer?</h2>
<p class="text-stone-600 font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">Most couples ask about price and availability. Here are the questions that actually distinguish good photographers from ones who'll frustrate you.</p>

