<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mt-10 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions About Maryland Wedding Planning Timelines</h2>

<details class="bg-white border border-rose-light/40 rounded-lg mb-3" open>
  <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 cursor-pointer">
    <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-charcoal">What's the most common mistake couples make in Maryland wedding planning?</h3>
  </summary>
  <div class="px-5 pb-5">
